title: Chippa Wilson Drop Out
description:
Chippa Wilson blew minds when he first threw down a big spin in the surf. With unique skate-style manuvers, Chippa is one of the leaders in surfing's aerial movement.

Chippa is rocking the Arnette Dropout in this clip, which is part of the A.C.E.S. collection. The Dropout features an extra set of interchangeable arms so people can create their own unique look to suit their mood. The arms are also compatible with the Dibs, Moolah and new Witch Doctor shades, giving people who back Arnette even more options for customization.

Stay in touch with Arnette for giveaways, as well as new team and product updates at www.facebook.com/arnette and www.arnette.com.
